<!-- Sección: Servicios y Procedimientos -->
<section class="services-section" id="servicios">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="services-showcase">
      <div class="services-column services-intro">
        <span class="section-subtitle">Servicios</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Atención quirúrgica clara, segura y especializada en Cuenca</h2>
        <p class="services-lead">Procedimientos de cirugía general y laparoscópica planificados con criterio médico, tecnología actual y seguimiento cercano en cada etapa.</p>

        <div class="services-assurance-list">
          <article class="services-assurance-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.55" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 21.5c5.2-2.4 7.8-5.8 7.8-10.3V5.4L12 2.5 4.2 5.4v5.8c0 4.5 2.6 7.9 7.8 10.3Z"/><path d="M12 7.2v8.6"/><path d="M7.7 11.5h8.6"/><path d="M9 16.4c1.8.9 4.2.9 6 0"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3>Valoración responsable</h3>
              <p>Se revisa cada caso antes de definir si conviene una técnica laparoscópica o convencional.</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="services-assurance-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.55" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3.5" y="4.5" width="17" height="16" rx="3"/><path d="M8 2.8v4M16 2.8v4M3.8 10h16.4"/><path d="M8 14.2h2.4M13.6 14.2H16M8 17.2h5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <h3>Consulta y seguimiento</h3>
              <p>Orientación antes del procedimiento y controles posteriores para una recuperación ordenada.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="services-column services-panel">
        <div class="services-pill">
          <span class="service-icon compact" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.65" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5.2 18.8 18.8 5.2"/><path d="m14.7 4.5 4.8 4.8"/><path d="m7.7 16.3-2.9 2.9"/><path d="M13.1 8.6 10 5.5"/><path d="m16 11.5-3.2 3.2"/></svg>
          </span>
          Cirugía general y mínima invasión
        </div>

        <div class="service-list">
          <article class="service-card featured">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.45" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5.2 18.8 18.8 5.2"/><path d="m14.7 4.5 4.8 4.8"/><path d="m7.8 16.2-3.1 3.1"/><path d="M12.7 9.1 9.4 5.8"/><path d="M15.7 12.1 12.4 15.4"/><path d="M10.3 13.7 8.9 12.3"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Cirugía laparoscópica</h3>
            <p class="service-short-desc">Alternativa mínimamente invasiva para resolver patologías abdominales con incisiones pequeñas.</p>
            <div class="service-full-desc hidden">
              <p>Busca reducir dolor, cicatrices y tiempo de recuperación cuando el diagnóstico permite este abordaje.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-service-more" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Ver más</span>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </button>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.45" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.5 4.2c2.1.8 3.4 2.4 3.8 4.6"/><path d="M14.3 8.8c1.4-.5 3.1-.2 4.1.9 1.9 2 1.5 6.2-1 8.8-2.6 2.8-6.7 3.5-9 1.4-1.9-1.8-1.9-5.1-.1-7.5"/><path d="M8.4 12.4c1.7 1.3 4.4 1.3 6.4-.1"/><path d="M10.1 16.2c1.2.6 2.8.6 4.1 0"/><path d="M8 4.2c-1.2 1.4-1.4 3-.5 4.5.7 1.2.7 2.3 0 3.5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Colecistectomía</h3>
            <p class="service-short-desc">Tratamiento quirúrgico para cálculos o inflamación de la vesícula biliar.</p>
            <div class="service-full-desc hidden">
              <p>La técnica se define luego de valorar síntomas, estudios de imagen y condición general del paciente.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-service-more" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Ver más</span>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </button>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.45" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6.5 6.5c1.4-1.4 3.3-1.6 5-.4 1.5 1 3.5.9 5-.3"/><path d="M6 10c1.5 1.2 3.3 1.2 5 .1 1.7-1.1 3.5-1 5.1.1"/><path d="M6.4 13.7c1.4 1.4 3.2 1.5 5 .4 1.7-1 3.5-.9 5 .4"/><path d="M7.5 17.4c1.5 1.5 3.8 2.1 6 1.4 2.5-.8 4.1-3 4.1-5.6 0-3.8-2.8-6.5-6.1-6.5-3.3 0-6.1 2.7-6.1 6.5 0 1.1.3 2.2.8 3.1"/><path d="M11.8 11.7c.9.9.9 2.5 0 3.4"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Cirugía de hernias</h3>
            <p class="service-short-desc">Corrección de hernias inguinales, umbilicales, epigástricas o de pared abdominal.</p>
            <div class="service-full-desc hidden">
              <p>Puede requerir técnica abierta o laparoscópica, con mallas quirúrgicas según la anatomía y el caso.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-service-more" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Ver más</span>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </button>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.45" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.6 3.5c2.6 1.3 4.2 3.8 4.2 6.9 0 3.6-2 6.3-5 8"/><path d="M14.9 4.6c2.2 2.4 3.2 5 3.2 8 0 2.6-.9 5.1-2.8 7.4"/><path d="M7 12.5c2.1-.5 4.4-.1 6.1 1.1"/><path d="M6.8 16.9c1.5-.6 3.2-.6 4.6.2"/><path d="M10.1 8.1c1.3.4 2.3 1.1 3 2.1"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Apendicectomía</h3>
            <p class="service-short-desc">Manejo quirúrgico de apendicitis aguda con enfoque oportuno y seguro.</p>
            <div class="service-full-desc hidden">
              <p>La atención temprana ayuda a disminuir complicaciones y permite planificar mejor la recuperación.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-service-more" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Ver más</span>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </button>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.45" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7.2 4.8c3-1.8 6.6-1.8 9.6 0"/><path d="M7.2 19.2c3 1.8 6.6 1.8 9.6 0"/><path d="M5 8.2c-.9 2.5-.9 5.1 0 7.6"/><path d="M19 8.2c.9 2.5.9 5.1 0 7.6"/><path d="M8.7 8.7h6.6v6.6H8.7z"/><path d="M8.7 12h6.6M12 8.7v6.6"/><path d="M10 10.1 14 14M14 10.1 10 14"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Pared abdominal</h3>
            <p class="service-short-desc">Evaluación y reparación de defectos de pared, eventraciones y diástasis seleccionadas.</p>
            <div class="service-full-desc hidden">
              <p>El objetivo es recuperar estabilidad abdominal, función y seguridad en las actividades diarias.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-service-more" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Ver más</span>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </button>
          </article>

          <article class="service-card">
            <span class="service-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.45" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8.3 19.3c-1.7-1.2-2.8-3.1-2.8-5.3 0-3.5 2.7-6.3 6.2-6.3 3.1 0 5.7 2.3 6.1 5.3"/><path d="M13.2 4.2c2 .6 3.4 2 4.2 3.9"/><path d="M10.4 11.2c1.4-1.1 3.5-1 4.8.2 1.5 1.4 1.6 3.8.2 5.3-1.3 1.4-3.4 1.7-5 .8"/><path d="M10.6 14.4h5.9"/><path d="M13.6 11.5v5.9"/></svg>
            </span>
            <h3>Lipomas y quistes</h3>
            <p class="service-short-desc">Retiro de lesiones superficiales seleccionadas bajo valoración médica previa.</p>
            <div class="service-full-desc hidden">
              <p>Se revisa tamaño, ubicación y características para indicar el procedimiento más adecuado.</p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-service-more" aria-expanded="false">
              <span>Ver más</span>
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </button>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="services-bottom-cta">
      <div>
        <span class="service-icon compact" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.65" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3.5" y="4.5" width="17" height="16" rx="3"/><path d="M8 2.8v4M16 2.8v4M3.8 10h16.4"/><path d="M8 14.2h2.4M13.6 14.2H16M8 17.2h5"/></svg>
        </span>
        <p><strong>¿Necesita orientación sobre su caso?</strong><br />Agende una valoración para revisar síntomas, exámenes y alternativas de tratamiento.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="services-cta-button" href="https://wa.me/593982757711?text=Hola%20Dr.%20Vintimilla,%20deseo%20agendar%20una%20consulta%20de%20valoración." target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3.5" y="4.5" width="17" height="16" rx="3"/><path d="M8 2.8v4M16 2.8v4M3.8 10h16.4"/><path d="M8 14.2h2.4M13.6 14.2H16"/></svg>
        Agendar consulta
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  // Add interactivity to the "Ver más" buttons on service cards
  document.querySelectorAll('.service-card').forEach(card => {
    const btn = card.querySelector('.btn-service-more');
    const fullDesc = card.querySelector('.service-full-desc');
    
    if (btn && fullDesc) {
      btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const isExpanded = btn.getAttribute('aria-expanded') === 'true';
        btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', (!isExpanded).toString());
        fullDesc.classList.toggle('hidden', isExpanded);
        
        const btnText = btn.querySelector('span');
        if (btnText) {
          btnText.textContent = isExpanded ? 'Ver más' : 'Ver menos';
        }
      });
    }
  });
</script>
